Common Resource Routes to be used for Controller
- index: show all resources (e.g., all anime)
- show: show a single resource (e.g., anime)
- create: show a form to create a new resource (e.g., new anime form)
- store: save a new resource to the database (e.g., save new anime to database)
- edit: show a form to edit a resource (e.g., edit anime form)
- update: save an edited resource to the database (e.g., save edited anime to database)
- destroy: delete a resource from the database (e.g., delete anime from database)
